They ain't no right on no paper. President or not can tell me what I can and can't do on my property. Get your shit. You dead shying and get the hell out of here. This is my land. You just ain't hearing me. You just ain't hearing me. Now goddamn it. Something tells me you ain't got the nerve to fire that woman. You
